ell-calibrated? Could it produce false positives?\n4. Does the subset dedup enhancement (food-category suffix protection) create any edge cases?\n5. Is the overall flow coherent — do the 4 fixes compose well without unintended interactions?\n\nRead the source file and the improvement plan, then provide your assessment.","uuid":"ac720251-9f1e-4235-909e-6c20e1e632ba","session_id":"66d6120a-7fee-4673-bb0a-75db3320d34d"}
