{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_019R3kFpqanAF8ridcgVZm1a","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HPYA7eLe1orHqY39Ex7h1D","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Testing quality review","subagent_type":"code-review-expert","prompt":"Review test quality for the title-extractor changes.\n\n## Context\nThe title extractor has been through 28 iterations of optimization. Changes include:\n1. Dual-variant blind OCR repair (i vs l variants)\n2. Direct-successor bonus skipping blank lines\n3. Broadened overflow marker regex\n4. Unified body-content prologue detector\n\n## Files to read\n- lib/text-classifier/__tests__/title-extractor.test.ts — the unit test file\n- lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts — the source (to understand what's testable)\n- tools/title-loop/docs/28-1ac016c/improvement-plan.md — the plan (describes expected test cases)\n\n## Focus Areas\n1. **Coverage of new functions** — Are `hasErraticCasing`, `normalizeErraticCasing`, `generateBlindOcrVariants`, `applyBlindOcrRepair`, `applyBlindOcrRepairToken` tested? They're not exported, so they'd need to be tested through the public API.\n2. **Edge cases for OCR repair** — Does the test suite cover: mixed `i`/`l` ambiguity, erratic casing like `KoPyTka`, ALL_CAPS repair, `¡→i` and `€→e` substitution?\n3. **Prologue detection** — Are there tests for interleaved instruction/prose patterns? For the blank-line-skipping in the direct-successor bonus?\n4. **Overflow markers** — Tests for `[CORRUPTED TEXT FROM PREVIOUS PAGE - PARTIAL RECIPE]` style markers?\n5. **Regression protection** — Given this is iteration 28, are the existing tests comprehensive enough to catch regressions from the 4 changes?\n6. **The eval suite** — The plan mentions `eval_only.py` for integration testing. Check if `tools/title-loop/eval_only.py` exists and what it does.\n7. **Test structure** — Is the mock embed function adequate? Does it cover the scoring nuances needed for the new variant comparison logic?\n\nProvide specific gaps and suggestions for new test cases."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1998,"cache_read_input_tokens":40068,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1998},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"66d6120a-7fee-4673-bb0a-75db3320d34d","uuid":"73a2c33e-c7f6-439b-838b-94c3f55cf743"}
